title: 1br Bedroom In Brand New Building, One Month Free Parking
posting_body: ['Amazing apartment available now at 1177 Market Apartments at Trinity Place!', 'Be an inaugural resident in the new downtown SF luxury building!', 'Call today to schedule a tour or reserve your new home.', 'show contact info', '<URL>/', '1x1 3D Tour (Copy & Paste Link)', '<URL>', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES', "8' – 11' ceiling heights", 'Huge windows', 'Fabulous views', 'Chef-inspired kitchens', 'Stainless steel appliances', 'Stone countertops', 'Wood-style floors', 'BUILDING AMENITIES', 'Grocery shopping is made easy with Whole Foods in the same building as your new home!', 'Fitness centers fully outfitted with cardio and strength training equipment', 'Convenient underground parking', 'Resident lounges with Wi-Fi', 'Bike storage', 'Several rooftop decks', '24-hour Front Desk Associates', 'Laundry Center on each floor', 'Pets Allowed (Dogs & Cats)', '24-hour Courtesy Patrol', 'NEIGHBORHOOD AMENITIES', 'Walking distance to Union Square and the Westfield Mall', 'Located across the street from the Heart of The City Farmer’s Market, open every Sunday and Wednesday, supporting 55 local farmers', 'Less than 1 mile from the Soma StrEat Food Park featuring food trucks and rotating vendors every week', 'ABOUT US', 'Trinity was founded in 1949 with a singular purpose—to become The City’s premier apartment provider.', 'Seven decades later, Trinity stands “best-in-class” with buildings that offer the best locations, prices, and amenities.', '<URL>', '<URL>', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by a tenant of their rights under the Rent Ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.']
